<body>

<h1>Steps>

<ol type="1">
<li>Open Microsoft Word.</li>

<li>Select the "Insert" tab at top of the page.</li>
<p><img src="1.jpg"></p>

<li>Select the "WordArt" drop down at the top right of the page under "Text" options.</li>
<p><img src="2.jpg"></p>

<li>Select the WordArt that you want to use, then edit the text.</li>
<p><img src="3.jpg"></p>
</ol>

